# nginx-ingress

```bash
# install
helm install ingress-nginx ingress-nginx/ingress-nginx

# run example
kubectl run --generator=run-pod/v1 my-nginx --image=nginx --port=80 --expose=true
kubectl create -f ingress/example-ingress.yaml

# now you can visit http://test.example.com

# cleanup
kubectl delete service my-nginx
kubectl delete pod my-nginx
kubectl delete -f ingress/example-ingress.yaml
```
